description: Sea dogs and tale spinners tell stories of a mythical siren that could lure even the stubbornest sailors to a watery grave.

spells.description:
Use: Inject an enemy with digestive venom, dealing 720,608 Nature damage over 20 sec. While active, your attacks and abilities against the target restore 37,532 health. Cannot occur more than every 1 sec. 

Overhealing from this effect permanently increases your maximum health by the same amount, becoming an absorb shield upon leaving combat. (1 Min 30 Sec Cooldown)

Equip: Your attacks have a chance to call to the pact, exploding for 131,947 Shadow damage split between nearby enemies and increasing your Haste by 890 for 10 sec.

Your death breaks the pact, causing a violent explosion.
